## 5. Cross-experiment synthesis

### 5.1 What is now established at scope

**[DERIVED from MEASURED results]**

- Kernel-authored content can be externally endorsed and functionally useful.
- Its F2 runtime effect is carried by correct item alignment.
- The generic aligned projection reproduces the kernel runtime exactly on the DECONF-B grid.
